room_title: Escape room "Left at Home" by The Quandary Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_address: 3205 N Clark St Suite 100, Chicago, IL 60657
room_description: Get into the Holiday spirit with a non-copyright infringing tale of a young man who is left HOME ALONE for the holidays. You are in the role of Cal McKevinister, an 8-year-old, living in the suburbs of Chicago. Your family has left on a vacation and has mistakenly left you HOME ALONE. Now you need to make plans and set traps to fend off neighborhood bandits who are trying to rob your house.
